{"tid":1164117,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四匪16秒劫商人178萬","createTime":"2019-05-21T00:28:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T14:35:17.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cff4c125522f15e3dba0a44679ca3d5fbe5feb74","tid":1164117,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:28:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190521/20683647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F20683647&d=Udlbz0MX%2FrD6%2BzJW%2FeuWbUtjIx4W8g%2FGk507jgkcous%3D&h=38bb3803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190521%2F20683647&h=f5d8835e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190521/20683647</a><br />\n<br />\n四匪16秒劫商人178萬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190521/large/21la5p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190521%2Flarge%2F21la5p6.jpg&h=257ab0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇劫男子事後送院。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名物流公司負責人身懷178萬元現金，準備到土瓜灣木廠街一間找換店兌換時，在熙來攘往街頭遭四名持刀及鐵通蒙面匪徒截劫，賊人搶去巨款後登上私家車逃去。附近店舖閉路電視拍到行劫經過，發現賊車在案發前約10分鐘已停在路邊守候，賊人見事主出現即落車打人搶錢，整個過程只用了16秒。警方懷疑賊人早已掌握事主資料，正追緝四名歹徒下落。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賊車守候 疑有內鬼<br />\n<br />\n遇劫男子姓譚（39歲），頭部及手部被打傷，據稱譚經營物流生意，常到木廠街與馬頭涌道交界一間找換店匯錢，案中被劫的178萬港元，部份是匯款到內地，其餘則兌換人民幣。由於譚不定時到該找換店，而店前更有警察簽到簿，警方相信劫匪事前曾踩線，並可能有消息知道譚行蹤，不排除是有內鬼協助。警方正追查案件並追緝四名賊人。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨午1時22分，當時涉案黑色私家車已泊在木廠街與譚公道交界的交通燈前，其間譚拿着一個盛有178萬元現金的黑色袋沿木廠街向馬頭涌道行走，車上四名蒙面男落車跑向行人路，四人分持利刀及鐵通向譚施襲，並搶走盛巨款的黑色袋，跳回車上絕塵逃去，全程只是16秒。譚頭部紅腫及手部擦傷，由救護員到場敷治及送院，警方封鎖現場調查，案件交由九龍城警區重案組接手。<br />\n<br />\n■記者翁鈺輝、黃麗英  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n律師墜機亡 百人蒐證撿殘肢<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n欠債青年被擄 警拘六男"},{"pid":"8b96ca8cd8cf7a6d2a7f0ef62d7fbbd797515c85","tid":1164117,"uid":40470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T00:30:36.000Z","msg":"物流公司做走水貨嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b4aa604c622cc1c8d2351b87e1312f23ae1336","tid":1164117,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:34:49.000Z","msg":"身懷178萬元現金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ffb412977d0c0fc1effa61d4ad92b49a99a2488","tid":1164117,"uid":28743,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:37:20.000Z","msg":"似係自己友做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d93eeaaebcf62585b52893b75770ef4274e87220","tid":1164117,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔知點解覺得成件事好膠，一來個負責人成個on9咁，二來一丁友帶咁多錢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4accec574e1957e6c5450c76508439eaf2898206","tid":1164117,"uid":58484,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4fb185b58fa5654e0858736b22236b27233c2da6","tid":1164117,"uid":45431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d93eeaaebcf62585b52893b75770ef4274e87220","tid":1164117,"uid":19126,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T01:37:30.000Z","msg":"唔知點解覺得成件事好膠，一來個負責人成個on9咁，二來一丁友帶咁多錢出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔識形容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"其應該係慣左，由十幾萬到幾十萬到百幾萬，日日都係咁行過附近錢莊出數，久而久之無左戒備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4678f8b5251